Database initialization commands

Usage: obsidian-cli-inspector init [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  init  Initialize or reinitialize the database
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -o, --output <FORMAT>  Output in JSON format (for machine integration)
  -h, --help             Print help
